{
  "id": "adv_event_2107_01_02",
  "title": "ジンクス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私はあの有名な水族館に行きたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like to go to that famous aquarium.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666666666665,
      "endTime": 7.899999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "せやな、沖縄観光するなら水族館はマストやねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If y'all head down to Okinawa‚ y'all gotta check out the dang aquarium!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "endTime": 13.099999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3,
      "endTime": 14.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "観光と言えば世界遺産は外せない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you mustn’t miss the World Heritage Sites…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.166666666666666,
      "endTime": 18.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "昔の城跡とかパワースポットな聖地とか\n沖縄は見所が沢山あるからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ol' castle ruins and them sacred power spots…\nOkinawa's got so many darn places to see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 25.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8,
      "endTime": 27.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私は沖縄の踊りを見てみたいわ\n手の動きに特徴があるのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see Okinawan dances.\nThey have those special hand movements‚ don’t they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.666666666666668,
      "endTime": 33.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "エイサーやカチャーシーやね\n一緒に踊るとめっちゃ盛り上がるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Eisa and Katcharsee dances.\nIt's a hoot to dance together with 'em.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 38.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私はシーサーが見たいな～\nシーサーって可愛いよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d love to see the Shisa lion dogs.\nThey’re so cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.93333333333333,
      "endTime": 44.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "シーサーはゆるキャラちゃうやん\nあと、さくらちゃんの可愛い基準おかしない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shisa ain't no mascot characters‚ I tell ya.\nAnd Sakura-chan‚ yer standards of cuteness are downright peculiar.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 50.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、さっきから不思議に思ってたんだけど\nどうして優がいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey… I’ve been thinking this.\nBut why is Yu here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 56.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "今はサニピの沖縄旅行の話し合い……\nなのに自然に輪に入ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re chatting about Sunny Peace’s trip to Okinawa…\nBut she has naturally joined in…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 62.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄旅行じゃなくてお仕事だよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn’t a trip to Okinawa‚ it’s a job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 65.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあえーやないの\nこう見えてもうちは沖縄について結構詳しいんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C'mon now‚ it don't matter none.\nYa wouldn't think so‚ but I sure do know a heap 'bout Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 72.52819372949502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 74.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、さっきから遙子さんはため息ばっかりで\n全然喋ってへんけど、どないしたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Haruko-san‚ why y'all keep sighin'?\nYa ain't sayin' a word. What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 81.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃん、沖縄行きが決まってから元気がないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been down ever since it was decided that we’re going to Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 85.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "理由を聞いても全然教えてくれないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if we ask you why‚ you don’t tell us anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 89.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……遙子さん、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Erm… Haruko-san‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 93.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、ごめんなさい\n何でもないから気にしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh‚ I’m sorry.\nIt’s nothing‚ so don’t worry about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "endTime": 98.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そない言われたら余計に気になるわ\nずっと上の空で何考えてるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ya sayin' that just makes me worry even more.\nIt's like yer driftin' off in space. What's on yer mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5,
      "endTime": 104.79999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In fact—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105,
      "endTime": 106.70000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "みんな一緒の仲間やろ？\n悩みがあるなら、みんなで解決した方がええで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're all friends together‚ right?\nIf somethin's botherin' ya‚ we can all solve it together‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9,
      "endTime": 113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そうよね。えっと……\n私は沖縄に行かない方がいいのかなって思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Erm…\nI think maybe it’s better if I don’t go to Okinawa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 122.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 125.09999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "……実は私、沖縄と相性が悪いの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I just don’t get along with Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3,
      "endTime": 130.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "相性が悪い？\n沖縄に相性なんてあるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y'all don't get along?\nWhat does gettin' along with Okinawa even mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4,
      "endTime": 135.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "昔、ソロ時代の仕事で沖縄に行ったことがあるの\nその時は野外ステージで歌う予定だったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went to Okinawa once‚ for work‚ back when I was solo.\nThat time‚ I was scheduled to sing on an outdoor stage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3,
      "endTime": 144.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "私が歌い始めたら突然スコールが降り出して\nお客さんがみんないなくなっちゃったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I started to sing‚ there was a sudden squall‚\nand all the audience ran away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145,
      "endTime": 151.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "私は土砂降りの雨に濡れながら\n誰もいない観客席に向かって歌ったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There I was‚ soaked to the skin in pouring rain‚\nsinging to empty seats.",
