      "text": "そ、それは災難やったね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what a disaster…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2,
      "endTime": 161.3333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "けど野外ライブで雨なんてよくある話やん\nそんなに気にせんでもええんちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But rainin' at an outdoor show is somethin' that happens a lot.\nIt ain't somethin' to worry 'bout so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 167.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
