      "text": "浜辺に作った特設ステージが暴風雨で吹き飛ばされて\n雨天決行のイベントだったのに、嵐で中止になったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The stage that was built on the beach was blown away by the rainstorm.\nThe event was to go ahead even if it rained‚ but that storm was enough to stop it.",
